content:
XamlGeneratedNamespace Namespace

Definition

Contains compiler-generated types that are not intended to be used directly from your code.

In this Article

Introduction

Do not use or include this namespace. The purpose of this namespace is a container for the GeneratedInternalTypeHelper class GeneratedInternalTypeHelper is an internal helper that the XAML markup compiler produces for XAML type resolution against assemblies.

Classes

GeneratedInternalTypeHelper

Provides infrastructure support for XAML markup compilers and developer tools.
